## Task 1: Backend Setup & Experiment APIs

Implemented a FastAPI backend to manage experiments through REST APIs.
This task establishes a clean backend foundation with proper request handling and API documentation.

Key highlights:

Clean API design

Swagger-based testing

Experiment lifecycle modeling

## Overview

Task 1 focuses on setting up the backend service using FastAPI and implementing REST APIs to manage experiments.
This task establishes the base for all subsequent tasks.

## Tech Stack

Python

FastAPI

Uvicorn

REST APIs

Swagger UI

How to Run
# Clone the repository
git clone <repository-url>
cd task1-project

# Create and activate virtual environment
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate   # Windows
# source venv/bin/activate  # Mac/Linux

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Start the server
uvicorn main:app --reload


Open Swagger UI:

http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs

